h.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1116dbc497179ee0b70a0b8831e1e86674f2f610","tid":1471152,"uid":116722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:02:17.000Z","msg":"推到有人理"},{"pid":"e2735254552c52ef440f0aa339adc88165a02168","tid":1471152,"uid":17443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:02:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無錯，環球時報證實係在採訪<br />\n即係工作中<br />\n只要佢唔係拎工作簽證入境已經拉得</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">入境處，做返一次人應該做既野</span>"},{"pid":"b62447ca8d18febc96c28c3dc2daf9ef8a65fcc4","tid":1471152,"uid":248326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:03:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果入境咁都唔拉 咁以後唔洗拉黑工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0def58cef888f68039f844003a7152137a040e","tid":1471152,"uid":116722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:05:01.000Z","msg":"唔執法姐係放生姐"},{"pid":"faf42eed1d0e6c61252053a91adea07fe30731f2","tid":1471152,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:05:05.000Z","msg":"如果告得入就正<br />\n所有自遊行嚟香港「開會」嘅都可以告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27b4a7b966e68e769c3593884fbf4ddcec4be70","tid":1471152,"uid":199797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:05:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1173acf8c157f21ebbddfa82d8c67bded6d78f3d","tid":1471152,"uid":289603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:09:01.000Z","msg":"（轉）<br />\n<br />\n王丹回應昨晚香港機場示威者捉拿環球時報記者事件：<br />\n<br />\n「1989年六四前夕，中共就曾經把一輛破舊的軍車丟棄在長安街上，然後把上車檢查的民眾誣指為「搶奪軍車，準備暴亂」，為六四開槍製造口實。<br />\n<br />\n現在中共故技重施，派一些人用苦肉計，故意挑釁示威民眾，拍下被毆打照片，在中國民眾中製造「香港人毆打中國人「的假新聞，也是為以後可能的鎮壓製造口實。<br />\n<br />\n我一個過來人，一看就知道中共要幹什麼。因此在這裡誠懇呼籲香港示威者：對於故意挑釁的人，不理他們便是，讓他們自我表演，把他們當空氣就好。<br />\n<br />\n同時也要呼籲外界一定要明辨是非：<br />\n<br />\n第一，我們要相信示威者的理性，相信他們不會無緣無故暴力攻擊無辜者。正常人都不可能自己給自己入罪。<br />\n<br />\n第二，我們一定要知道，很多暴力衝突，其實是中共派人假裝成示威者所為。這方面，他們是慣犯。」"},{"pid":"60b59ede96ddf444fecd441ffabd374fe76ca05c","tid":1471152,"uid":17443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"faf42eed1d0e6c61252053a91adea07fe30731f2","tid":1471152,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:05:05.000Z","msg":"如果告得入就正<br />\n所有自遊行嚟香港「開會」嘅都可以告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:09:17.000Z","msg":"台灣model私影呢？"},{"pid":"b515d86d6d5530fd84a039707b7480f46bace3b0","tid":1471152,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60b59ede96ddf444fecd441ffabd374fe76ca05c","tid":1471152,"uid":17443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"faf42eed1d0e6c61252053a91adea07fe30731f2","tid":1471152,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:05:05.000Z","msg":"如果告得入就正<br />\n所有自遊行嚟香港「開會」嘅都可以告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:09:17.000Z","msg":"台灣model私影呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3583426474458b3468e0917c6b9d848e5b8ce52f","tid":1471152,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead